 The beautiful region of Cologne in Germany might not be the most obvious homeplace for drum & bass, but if the jazzy inspirations and deep rolling basslines of Marvel Cinema's tunes have taught us anything, it's that you should never judge a book by its cover.
 This is their debut full-length LP release, and Liquid Drops have really hit a home run grabbing it. A full selection of melodious emotional tracks, deep rollers, heavy steppers and dancefloor fillers, this is a liquid fan's dream. Pick this up and fall in love with the genre all over again.
